Name: The Space Eater (Working Title)
About the game: The Space Eater is a mystery adventure game inspired by classic horror RPG Maker games. Investigate your surroundings for clues, solve puzzles and move forward. Take control of a mysterious man and a suspicious hotelier to explore a mysterious hotel. You must navigate through the metaphorical spaces of the hotel, face dark secrets, and find the monsters hiding in its gaps.
